## 防抖&节流

防抖：

```js

function debounce(fn,delay){
    let timer = 0;
    if(!timer){
        timer = setTimeout(()=>{
            fn.apply(this,arguments)
            timer = 0
        },delay)
    }
}


```


节流：
function debounce(fn,delay){
    let timer = 0;
    if(timer){
         return 
    }
    timer = setTimeout(()=>{
            fn.apply(this,arguments)
            timer = 0
      },delay)
}

```



